SL-Client version 0.1
============================

This library provides the necessary software for Silver Lining clients.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  perl 5.8.5
  Apache::Test
  mod_perl 2.0

